<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Servizio non disponibile - HelpDigit</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .maintenance-container {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-db {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .error-code {
            font-family: monospace;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <div class="container maintenance-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
                <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                    <div class="card-body p-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-database icon-db"></i>
                        <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Servizio temporaneamente non disponibile</h1>
                        <p class="lead mb-4">Ci scusiamo, ma il nostro database Ã¨ attualmente sovraccarico.</p>
                        <p>Stiamo lavorando per risolvere il problema. Riprova tra qualche minuto.</p>
                        
                        <% if (typeof errorCode !== 'undefined' && errorCode) { %>
                            <div class="mt-4">
                                <p>Se il problema persiste, contatta l'assistenza citando il codice:</p>
                                <span class="error-code"><%= errorCode %></span>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                                <i class="fas fa-home mr-2"></i>Torna alla Home
                            </a>
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary ml-3" onclick="window.location.reload()">
                                <i class="fas fa-sync-alt mr-2"></i>Riprova
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Auto-reload dopo 10 secondi
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.reload();
        }, 10000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>